snippet.title: 2XKO (Formerly Project L)Gameplay Basics & Tag - /dev diary
snippet.description:
Executive producer Tom Cannon and game director Shaun Rivera give an in-depth look at 2XKO (Formerly Project L)'s gameplay and tag systems and an update on Illaoi.

Learn more about 2XKO (Formerly Project L): https://youtu.be/BbwmX-coQCM & https://youtu.be/5hugGCZon3I

Creator-safe music:
Pulse - Dilip from Sessions: Diana
Listen: https://youtu.be/mtv8WkYyK0s?t=1824
Ascent - Puurple Cat from Sessions: Diana
Listen: https://youtu.be/mtv8WkYyK0s?t=6221
MOCHI - Bear Bear & Friends from Sessions: Taliyah
Listen: https://youtu.be/uc461NBBqWs?t=5473
Shimmer City - TANUKI from Sessions: Taliyah
Listen: https://youtu.be/uc461NBBqWs?t=3279
Moonphaze - Suteki from Sessions: Diana
Listen: https://youtu.be/mtv8WkYyK0s?t=2427
